channel.title: Problem With My Cache
channel.description:
Hello Mopar,
I've been having a problem with my auto cache downloader recently. I have the full cache packaged into a .zip file in my dropbox, and my autocachedownloader is linked to it - but when it goes to auto download it, it says
"Unable to Load/Download TrisidiaX Cache..."
and The Downloaded cache looks like this:
http://prntscr.com/19g7su
I've tried just about everything, so if anyone could help me out over teamviewer, it would be nice.
Thanks, Tragedy
